{[%evp 0,23,26,26,24,-3,12,4,44,47,48,53,32,-8,28,38,21,0,27,-12,-32,-21,-22,-25,-14,-70]} 13. Ne4 $1 Qa5+ 14. b4 $1 Qd8 (14... Nxb4 $6 15. O-O Re8 16. Qd2 c5 17. Bxe7 Rxe7 18. Rad1 f5 (18... Re8 19. Qg5 $18 {[%cal Gg1h1,Gf1g1]}) 19. Qd8+ Qxd8 20. Rxd8+ Kf7 21. Nd6+ Kf6 22. Rd1 $1 $14) 15. Rg1 Ng6 (15... f6 $6 {[%cal Ge6e5] Venkatesan,K (2202)-Smeets,K (2322) Prague CZE 2024} 16. Qe2 $1 {After this move, Black's position completely collapses.} Nf5 (16... Nc7 17. O-O-O Ne8 18. Bc5 Qc7 19. Nd6 $18) (16... e5 17. O-O-O $18) 17. O-O-O $1 Rf7 (17... Nxd6 18. Nxd6 $18) 18. Bh5 $1 Rd7 19. Qg4 Nc7 (19... Kh8 20. Bg6 $3 $18) 20. Bxc7 Qxc7 21. Nxf6+ Kh8 22. Nxd7 $18) 16. h4 $1 $40 (16. Bxf8 Qxf8 17. a3 e5 18. Qd6 $13 {[%cal Ga1d1,Gb4b5] also looks good for White.}) *

